<h3>Must-include terms</h3>

<div class="ds_accordion" data-module="ds-accordion">
    <button  type="button" class="ds_link  ds_accordion__open-all  js-open-all">Open all <span class="visually-hidden">sections</span></button>

    <div class="ds_accordion-item">
        <input type="checkbox" class="visually-hidden  ds_accordion-item__control" id="panel-tenants{% if mandatory2 %}-2{% endif %}" aria-labelledby="panel-tenants-heading" />
        <div class="ds_accordion-item__header">
            <h3 id="panel-tenants-heading" class="ds_accordion-item__title">
                Tenant(s)
            </h3>
            <span class="ds_accordion-item__indicator"></span>
            <label class="ds_accordion-item__label" for="panel-tenants{% if mandatory2 %}-2{% endif %}"><span class="visually-hidden">Show this section</span></label>
        </div>

        <div class="ds_accordion-item__body" id="accordion-item-tenants">
            {% if hasTenants %}

                <p>Name(s) and Address(es):</p>

                <ol>
                {% for key, tenant in tenants %}
                    {% if tenant.name %}
                    <li>
                        <span class="summary__user-input">
                        {{tenant.name | notspecified | safe}}<br></span>
                        <span class="summary__user-input blank-if-empty"><!--
                        -->{% if tenant.address.building %}{{tenant.address.building}}<br>{% endif %}<!--
                        -->{% if tenant.address.street %}{{tenant.address.street}}<br>{% endif %}<!--
                        -->{% if tenant.address.town %}{{tenant.address.town}}<br>{% endif %}<!--
                        -->{% if tenant.address.region %}{{tenant.address.region}}<br>{% endif %}<!--
                        -->{% if tenant.address.postcode %}{{tenant.address.postcode}}{% endif %}<!--
                        --></span>
                    </li>
                    {% endif %}
                {% endfor %}
                </ol>

                <p>(“the Tenant(s)”)</p>

                <p>Where this is a joint tenancy, the term “Tenant” applies to each of the individuals above and the full responsibilities and rights set out in this Agreement apply to each Tenant who will be jointly and severally liable for all of the obligations of the Tenant under this Agreement. </p>

                <p>Email address(es):</p>

                <ol>
                {% for key, tenant in tenants %}
                    {% if tenant.name %}
                        <li><span class="summary__user-input">{{tenant.email | notspecified | safe}}</span></li>
                    {% endif %}
                {% endfor %}
                </ol>

                <p>Telephone number(s)</p>

                <ol>
                {% for key, tenant in tenants %}
                    {% if tenant.name %}
                        <li><span class="summary__user-input">{{tenant.telephone | notspecified | safe}}</span></li>
                    {% endif %}
                {% endfor %}
                </ol>

            {% else %}

                <p>No tenants specified.</p>

            {% endif %}
        </div>
    </div>

    {% if (hasLettingAgent == 'yes') %}
    <div class="ds_accordion-item">
        <input type="checkbox" class="visually-hidden  ds_accordion-item__control" id="panel-letting-agent{% if mandatory2 %}-2{% endif %}" aria-labelledby="panel-letting-agent-heading" />
        <div class="ds_accordion-item__header">
            <h3 id="panel-letting-agent-heading" class="ds_accordion-item__title">
                Letting agent
            </h3>
            <span class="ds_accordion-item__indicator"></span>
            <label class="ds_accordion-item__label" for="panel-letting-agent{% if mandatory2 %}-2{% endif %}"><span class="visually-hidden">Show this section</span></label>
        </div>

        <div class="ds_accordion-item__body" id="accordion-item-letting-agent">
            <p>Name: <span class="summary__user-input">{{ lettingAgent.name | notspecified | safe}}</span></p>

            <p>Address: <br>
            <span class="summary__user-input blank-if-empty"><!--
            -->{% if lettingAgent.address.building %}{{lettingAgent.address.building}}<br>{% endif %}<!--
            -->{% if lettingAgent.address.street %}{{lettingAgent.address.street}}<br>{% endif %}<!--
            -->{% if lettingAgent.address.town %}{{lettingAgent.address.town}}<br>{% endif %}<!--
            -->{% if lettingAgent.address.region %}{{lettingAgent.address.region}}<br>{% endif %}<!--
            -->{% if lettingAgent.address.postcode %}{{lettingAgent.address.postcode}}{% endif %}</span></p>

            <p>Telephone number: <span class="summary__user-input">{{lettingAgent.telephone | notspecified | safe}}</span></p>

            <p>Registration number: <span class="summary__user-input">{{ lettingAgent.registrationNumber | notspecified | safe}}</span></p>

            <p>Email address: <span class="summary__user-input">{{ lettingAgent.email | notspecified | safe}}</span></p>

            <p>The above-named Agent will deliver the following services on behalf of the Landlord:</p>
            <ul class="blank-if-empty"><!--
                -->{% for service in servicesProvidedByLettingAgent %}<!--
                --><li><span class="summary__user-input">{{service.name}}</span> {% if (lettingAgentIsFirstContact == 'YES') %}<span class="summary__user-input">(letting agent is first point of contact)</span>{% endif %}</li><!--
                -->{% endfor %}<!--
            --></ul>

            <p>The Agent is the first point of contact for the following things:</p>
            <ul class="blank-if-empty"><!--
                -->{% for service in servicesLettingAgentIsFirstContactFor %}<!--
                    --><li><span class="summary__user-input">{{service.name}}</span></li><!--
                -->{% endfor %}<!--
            --></ul>
        </div>
    </div>
    {% endif %}

    <div class="ds_accordion-item">
        <input type="checkbox" class="visually-hidden  ds_accordion-item__control" id="panel-landlords{% if mandatory2 %}-2{% endif %}" aria-labelledby="panel-landlords-heading" />
        <div class="ds_accordion-item__header">
            <h3 id="panel-landlords-heading" class="ds_accordion-item__title">
                Landlord(s)
            </h3>
            <span class="ds_accordion-item__indicator"></span>
            <label class="ds_accordion-item__label" for="panel-landlords{% if mandatory2 %}-2{% endif %}"><span class="visually-hidden">Show this section</span></label>
        </div>

        <div class="ds_accordion-item__body" id="accordion-item-landlords">
            {% if hasLandlords %}

                <ol>
                {% for key, landlord in landlords %}
                    {% if landlord.name %}
                    <li>Name: <span class="summary__user-input">{{landlord.name | notspecified | safe}}</span></li>
                    {% endif %}
                {% endfor %}
                </ol>
                (“the Landlord(s)”)</p>

                <ol>
                {% for key, landlord in landlords %}
                    {% if landlord.name %}
                    <li>
                        Address: <br>
                        <span class="summary__user-input blank-if-empty"><!--
                        -->{% if landlord.address.building %}{{landlord.address.building}}<br>{% endif %}<!--
                        -->{% if landlord.address.street %}{{landlord.address.street}}<br>{% endif %}<!--
                        -->{% if landlord.address.town %}{{landlord.address.town}}<br>{% endif %}<!--
                        -->{% if landlord.address.region %}{{landlord.address.region}}<br>{% endif %}<!--
                        -->{% if landlord.address.postcode %}{{landlord.address.postcode}}{% endif %}</span>
                    </li>
                    {% endif %}
                {% endfor %}
                </ol>

                <p>Email address(es): </p>
                <ol>
                {% for key, landlord in landlords %}
                    {% if landlord.name %}
                    <li><span class="summary__user-input">{{landlord.email | notspecified | safe}}</span></li>
                    {% endif %}
                {% endfor %}
                </ol>

                <p>Telephone number(s): </p>
                <ol>
                {% for key, landlord in landlords %}
                    {% if landlord.name %}
                    <li><span class="summary__user-input">{{landlord.telephone | notspecified | safe}}</span></li>
                    {% endif %}
                {% endfor %}
                </ol>

                {% for key, landlord in landlords %}
                    {% if landlord.name %}
                    <p>Registration number (Landlord {{loop.index}}): <span class="summary__user-input">{{landlord.registrationNumber | notspecified | safe}}</span></p>
                    {% endif %}
                {% endfor %}

            {% else %}

                <p>No landlords specified.</p>

            {% endif %}
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="ds_accordion-item">
        <input type="checkbox" class="visually-hidden  ds_accordion-item__control" id="panel-communications{% if mandatory2 %}-2{% endif %}" aria-labelledby="panel-communications-heading" />
        <div class="ds_accordion-item__header">
            <h3 id="panel-communications-heading" class="ds_accordion-item__title">
                Communication
            </h3>
            <span class="ds_accordion-item__indicator"></span>
            <label class="ds_accordion-item__label" for="panel-communications{% if mandatory2 %}-2{% endif %}"><span class="visually-hidden">Show this section</span></label>
        </div>

        <div class="ds_accordion-item__body" id="accordion-item-communications">
            <p> The Landlord and Tenant agree that all communications which may or must be made under the Private Housing (Tenancies) (Scotland) Act 2016 and in relation to this Agreement, including notices to be served by one party on the other will be made in writing using <span class="summary__user-input" style="text-transform: lowercase;">
            {% if (communicationsAgreement == 'EMAIL') %}[the email addresses set out in clauses [2 or 3] and 1]{% endif %}
            {% if (communicationsAgreement == 'HARDCOPY') %}hard copy by personal delivery or recorded delivery{% endif %}
            {% if (communicationsAgreement == null) %}[the email addresses set out in clauses [2 or 3] and 1]/hard copy by personal delivery or recorded delivery{% endif %}</span>.</p>

            {% if (communicationsAgreement == 'EMAIL') %}
            <p>For communication by email it is essential that the Landlord(s) and Tenant(s) consider carefully whether this option is suitable for them.  It should be noted that all notices will be sent by email, which includes important documents such as a rent-increase notice and a notice to leave the Let Property.</p>

            <p>To ensure all emails can be received and read in good time, the Landlord(s) and Tenant(s) agree to inform each other as soon as possible of any new email address which is to be used instead of the email address notified in this Agreement. </p>
            {% endif %}
            {% if (communicationsAgreement == null) %}
            <p>For communication by email it is essential that the Landlord(s) and Tenant(s) consider carefully whether this option is suitable for them.  It should be noted that all notices will be sent by email, which includes important documents such as a rent-increase notice and a notice to leave the Let Property.</p>

            <p>To ensure all emails can be received and read in good time, the Landlord(s) and Tenant(s) agree to inform each other as soon as possible of any new email address which is to be used instead of the email address notified in this Agreement. </p>
            {% endif %}

            <p>If sending a document electronically or by recorded delivery post, the document will be regarded as having been received 48 hours after it was sent, unless the receiving party can provide proof that he or she received it later than this.  This extra delivery time should be factored into any required notice periods.   </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="ds_accordion-item">
        <input type="checkbox" class="visually-hidden  ds_accordion-item__control" id="panel-let-property{% if mandatory2 %}-2{% endif %}" aria-labelledby="panel-let-property-heading" />
        <div class="ds_accordion-item__header">
            <h3 id="panel-let-property-heading" class="ds_accordion-item__title">
                Details of the Let Property
            </h3>
            <span class="ds_accordion-item__indicator"></span>
            <label class="ds_accordion-item__label" for="panel-let-property{% if mandatory2 %}-2{% endif %}"><span class="visually-hidden">Show this section</span></label>
        </div>

        <div class="ds_accordion-item__body" id="accordion-item-let-property">
            <p>Address: <br>
            <span class="summary__user-input">
                {{ propertyAddress | notspecified | safe}}
            </span><br>
            (“the Let Property”)</p>

            <p>Type of property: <span class="summary__user-input">{{ propertyType_text | notspecified | safe}}
            {% if (propertyType == 'OTHER') %}
                {% if buildingOther %}
                    ({{ buildingOther | notspecified | safe}})
                {% endif %}
            {% endif %}</span></p>

            <p>Any other areas/facilities included with the Let Property:</p>
            <ul class="blank-if-empty"><!--
                -->{% for facility in facilities %}<!--
                    -->{% if (facility.type == 'INCLUDED') %}<!--
                        --><li><span class="summary__user-input">{{facility.name}}</span></li><!--
                    -->{% endif %}<!--
                -->{% endfor %}<!--
            --></ul>

            <p>Any shared areas/facilities:</p>
            <ul class="blank-if-empty"><!--
                -->{% for facility in facilities %}<!--
                -->{% if (facility.type == 'SHARED') %}<!--
                        --><li><span class="summary__user-input">{{facility.name}}</span></li><!--
                    -->{% endif %}<!--
                -->{% endfor %}<!--
            --></ul>

            <p>Any excluded areas/facilities:</p>
            <ul class="blank-if-empty"><!--
                -->{% for facility in facilities %}<!--
                -->{% if (facility.type == 'EXCLUDED') %}<!--
                        --><li><span class="summary__user-input">{{facility.name}}</span></li><!--
                    -->{% endif %}<!--
                -->{% endfor %}<!--
            --></ul>

            <p>The Let Property is <span class="summary__user-input" style="text-transform: lowercase;">{{ furnishingType_text | notspecified | safe}}</span>.  See the Inventory and Record of Condition for further details.</p>

            <p>The Let Property <span class="summary__user-input">{% if (inRentPressureZone == true) %}is{% endif %}{% if (inRentPressureZone == false) %}is not{% endif %}{% if (inRentPressureZone == null) %}[is not/is]{% endif %}</span> located in a rent pressure zone. </p>

            <p>If Scottish Ministers have designated the area that the Let Property is located in as a rent pressure zone, there will be a cap on the amount that the rent can be increased.  You can check whether the Let Property shown above is located in a rent pressure zone on the Scottish Government’s website <a href="https://www.mygov.scot/rent-pressure-zone-checker/" target="_blank">https://www.mygov.scot/rent-pressure-zone-checker/ (opens in a new window)</a>.</p>

            <p>The Let Property <span class="summary__user-input">{% if (hmoProperty == 'true') %}is{% endif %}{% if (hmoProperty == 'false') %}is not{% endif %}{% if (hmoProperty == null) %}[is not/is]{% endif %}</span> a House in Multiple Occupation (HMO).</p>

            {% if (hmoProperty == 'true') %}
            <p>HMO 24-hour contact number: <span class="summary__user-input">{{ hmo24ContactNumber | notspecified | safe }}</span></p>

            <p>HMO licence expiry date: <span class="summary__user-input">{{ hmoRegistrationExpiryDate | notspecified | safe }}</span></p>
            {% endif %}
            {% if (hmoProperty == null) %}
            <p>HMO 24-hour contact number: <span class="summary__user-input">{{ hmo24ContactNumber | notspecified | safe }}</span></p>

            <p>HMO licence expiry date: <span class="summary__user-input">{{ hmoRegistrationExpiryDate | notspecified | safe }}</span></p>
            {% endif %}
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="ds_accordion-item">
        <input type="checkbox" class="visually-hidden  ds_accordion-item__control" id="panel-tenancy-start-date{% if mandatory2 %}-2{% endif %}" aria-labelledby="panel-tenancy-start-date-heading" />
        <div class="ds_accordion-item__header">
            <h3 id="panel-tenancy-start-date-heading" class="ds_accordion-item__title">
                Start date of the tenancy
            </h3>
            <span class="ds_accordion-item__indicator"></span>
            <label class="ds_accordion-item__label" for="panel-tenancy-start-date{% if mandatory2 %}-2{% endif %}"><span class="visually-hidden">Show this section</span></label>
        </div>

        <div class="ds_accordion-item__body" id="accordion-item-tenancy-start-date">
            <p>The private residential tenancy will start on: <span class="summary__user-input">{{ tenancyStartDate | notspecified | safe }}</span> (“the start date of the tenancy”).</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="ds_accordion-item">
        <input type="checkbox" class="visually-hidden  ds_accordion-item__control" id="panel-let-property-occupation{% if mandatory2 %}-2{% endif %}" aria-labelledby="panel-let-property-occupation-heading" />
        <div class="ds_accordion-item__header">
            <h3 id="panel-let-property-occupation-heading" class="ds_accordion-item__title">
                Occupation and use of the Let Property
            </h3>
            <span class="ds_accordion-item__indicator"></span>
            <label class="ds_accordion-item__label" for="panel-let-property-occupation{% if mandatory2 %}-2{% endif %}"><span class="visually-hidden">Show this section</span></label>
        </div>

        <div class="ds_accordion-item__body" id="accordion-item-let-property-occupation">
            <p>The Tenant agrees to continue to occupy the Let Property as his or her home and must obtain the Landlord’s written permission before carrying out any trade, business or profession there.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="ds_accordion-item">
        <input type="checkbox" class="visually-hidden  ds_accordion-item__control" id="panel-rent{% if mandatory2 %}-2{% endif %}" aria-labelledby="panel-rent-heading" />
        <div class="ds_accordion-item__header">
            <h3 id="panel-rent-heading" class="ds_accordion-item__title">
                Rent
            </h3>
            <span class="ds_accordion-item__indicator"></span>
            <label class="ds_accordion-item__label" for="panel-rent{% if mandatory2 %}-2{% endif %}"><span class="visually-hidden">Show this section</span></label>
        </div>

        <div class="ds_accordion-item__body" id="accordion-item-rent">
            <p>The rent is £<span class="summary__user-input">{{ rentAmount | notspecified | safe }}
            {% if (rentPaymentFrequency == 'WEEKLY') %}a week{% endif %}
            {% if (rentPaymentFrequency == 'FORTNIGHTLY') %}a fortnight{% endif %}
            {% if (rentPaymentFrequency == 'EVERY_FOUR_WEEKS') %}every four weeks{% endif %}
            {% if (rentPaymentFrequency == 'CALENDAR_MONTH') %}a calendar month{% endif %}
            {% if (rentPaymentFrequency == 'QUARTERLY') %}a quarter{% endif %}
            {% if (rentPaymentFrequency == 'EVERY_SIX_MONTHS') %}every six months{% endif %}
            {% if (rentPaymentFrequency == '') %}<span class="summary__blank" title="not specified"></span>{% endif %}
            </span>
             payable in <span class="summary__user-input blank-if-empty" style="text-transform: lowercase;">{% if (rentPayableInAdvance == 'true') %}advance{% endif %}{% if (rentPayableInAdvance == 'false') %}arrears{% endif %}</span>.</p>

            <p>The first payment will be paid on <span class="summary__user-input">{{ firstPaymentDate | notspecified | safe }}</span> and will be for the sum of £<span class="summary__user-input">{{ firstPaymentAmount | notspecified | safe }}</span> in respect of the period <span class="summary__user-input">{{ tenancyStartDate | notspecified | safe }}</span> to <span class="summary__user-input">{{ firstPaymentPeriodEnd | notspecified | safe }}</span>. (The maximum amount of rent which can be paid in advance is 6 months' rent).</p>

            <p>Thereafter payments of £<span class="summary__user-input" style="text-transform: lowercase;">{{ rentAmount | notspecified | safe }}</span> must be received on <span class="summary__user-input">
            {% if (rentPaymentFrequency == 'WEEKLY') %}{{ rentPaymentScheduleObject.day | notspecified | safe }}{% endif %}
            {% if (rentPaymentFrequency == 'FORTNIGHTLY') %}{{ rentPaymentScheduleObject.day | notspecified | safe }} of the <span style="text-transform: lowercase;">{{ rentPaymentScheduleObject.week | notspecified | safe }}</span>{% endif %}
            {% if (rentPaymentFrequency == 'EVERY_FOUR_WEEKS') %}{{ rentPaymentScheduleObject.day | notspecified | safe }} of the <span style="text-transform: lowercase;">{{ rentPaymentScheduleObject.week | notspecified | safe }}</span>{% endif %}
            {% if (rentPaymentFrequency == 'CALENDAR_MONTH') %}the {{ rentPaymentScheduleObject.date | notspecified | safe }} of the month{% endif %}
            {% if (rentPaymentFrequency == 'QUARTERLY') %} the {{ rentPaymentScheduleObject.date | notspecified | safe }}{% endif %}
            {% if (rentPaymentFrequency == 'EVERY_SIX_MONTHS') %} the {{ rentPaymentScheduleObject.date | notspecified | safe }}{% endif %}
            {% if (rentPaymentFrequency == '') %}<span class="summary__blank" title="not specified"></span>{% endif %}</span>
             and then subsequently on or before the same <span class="summary__user-input blank-if-empty"><!--
            -->{% if (rentPaymentFrequency == 'WEEKLY') %}day of each week{% endif %}<!--
            -->{% if (rentPaymentFrequency == 'FORTNIGHTLY') %}day of each fortnight{% endif %}<!--
            -->{% if (rentPaymentFrequency == 'EVERY_FOUR_WEEKS') %}day of each four weekly period{% endif %}<!--
            -->{% if (rentPaymentFrequency == 'CALENDAR_MONTH') %}date each calendar month{% endif %}<!--
            -->{% if (rentPaymentFrequency == 'QUARTERLY') %}date each quarter{% endif %}<!--
            -->{% if (rentPaymentFrequency == 'EVERY_SIX_MONTHS') %}date each 6-month period{% endif %}<!--
            --></span> thereafter. </p>

            <p>Method by which rent is to be paid: <span class="summary__user-input">{{ rentPaymentMethod_text | notspecified | safe }}</span> <br>
            (This is the preferred method but rent may be paid using another method if it is reasonable in the circumstances.)</p>

            <p>The following services are included in the rent amount noted above:</p>
            <ul class="blank-if-empty"><!--
            -->{% for service in servicesIncludedInRent %}<!--
                    --><li class="hide-if-empty"><span class="summary__user-input">{{service.name}}{% if service.name %} - {% endif %}£{{service.value}}</span></li><!--
                -->{% endfor %}<!--
            --></ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="ds_accordion-item">
        <input type="checkbox" class="visually-hidden  ds_accordion-item__control" id="panel-rent-reciepts{% if mandatory2 %}-2{% endif %}" aria-labelledby="panel-rent-reciepts-heading" />
        <div class="ds_accordion-item__header">
            <h3 id="panel-rent-reciepts-heading" class="ds_accordion-item__title">
                Rent receipts
            </h3>
            <span class="ds_accordion-item__indicator"></span>
            <label class="ds_accordion-item__label" for="panel-rent-reciepts{% if mandatory2 %}-2{% endif %}"><span class="visually-hidden">Show this section</span></label>
        </div>

        <div class="ds_accordion-item__body" id="accordion-item-rent-reciepts">
            <p>Where any payment of rent is made in cash, the Landlord must provide the Tenant with a dated written receipt for the payment stating: the amount paid, and either (as the case may be) the amount which remains outstanding, or confirmation that no further amount remains outstanding. </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="ds_accordion-item">
        <input type="checkbox" class="visually-hidden  ds_accordion-item__control" id="panel-rent-increases{% if mandatory2 %}-2{% endif %}" aria-labelledby="panel-rent-increases-heading" />
        <div class="ds_accordion-item__header">
            <h3 id="panel-rent-increases-heading" class="ds_accordion-item__title">
                Rent increases
            </h3>
            <span class="ds_accordion-item__indicator"></span>
            <label class="ds_accordion-item__label" for="panel-rent-increases{% if mandatory2 %}-2{% endif %}"><span class="visually-hidden">Show this section</span></label>
        </div>

        <div class="ds_accordion-item__body" id="accordion-item-rent-increases">
            <p>The rent cannot be increased more than once in any twelve month period and the Landlord must give the Tenant at least three months’ notice before any increase can take place.  In order to increase the rent, the Landlord must give the Tenant a rent-increase notice, the content of which is set out in ‘The Private Residential Tenancies (Prescribed Notices and Forms) (Scotland) Regulations 2017’. The notice will be sent using the communication method agreed in the ‘Communication’ clause above.</p>

            <p>Within 21 days of receiving a rent-increase notice, the Tenant can refer the increase to a rent officer for adjudication if he or she considers that the rent increase amount is unreasonable, unless the property is located in a rent pressure zone (RPZ).  Before submitting a referral to a rent officer for rent adjudication, the Tenant must complete Part 3 of the rent-increase notice and return it to his or her Landlord to notify the Landlord of his or her intention to make a referral to a rent officer.   Failure to return Part 3 to the Landlord will mean that the rent increase will take effect from the date proposed in the notice.</p>

            <p>If the Let property is located within a rent pressure zone, the Tenant cannot refer a rent increase to a rent officer as Scottish Ministers will have set a cap on the maximum amount the rent can be increased.  </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="ds_accordion-item">
        <input type="checkbox" class="visually-hidden  ds_accordion-item__control" id="panel-deposit{% if mandatory2 %}-2{% endif %}" aria-labelledby="panel-deposit-heading" />
        <div class="ds_accordion-item__header">
            <h3 id="panel-deposit-heading" class="ds_accordion-item__title">
                Deposit
            </h3>
            <span class="ds_accordion-item__indicator"></span>
            <label class="ds_accordion-item__label" for="panel-deposit{% if mandatory2 %}-2{% endif %}"><span class="visually-hidden">Show this section</span></label>
        </div>

        <div class="ds_accordion-item__body" id="accordion-item-deposit">
            <p>The Landlord must lodge any deposit they receive with a tenancy deposit scheme within 30 working days of the start date of the tenancy.</p>

            <p>A tenancy deposit scheme is an independent third-party scheme approved by the Scottish Ministers to hold and protect a deposit until it is due to be repaid.</p>

            <p>At the start date of the tenancy or before, a deposit of £<span class="summary__user-input">{{ depositAmount | notspecified | safe }}</span> will be paid by the Tenant to the Landlord.  The Landlord will issue a receipt for the deposit to the Tenant.  No interest shall be paid by the Landlord to the Tenant for the deposit.</p>

            <p>By law, the deposit amount cannot exceed the equivalent of two months’ rent and cannot include any premiums. For example, charging for an administration fee or taking a holding fee (regardless of whether or not the holding fee is refundable).</p>

            <p>The scheme administrator is <span class="summary__user-input">{{ tenancyDepositSchemeAdministrator | notspecified | safe }}</span> and their contact details are: </p>

            <p><span class="summary__user-input">{% if tenancyDepositSchemeAdministrator %}{% else %}<span class="summary__blank" title="not specified"></span><br>{% endif %}
            {% if (tenancyDepositSchemeAdministrator == 'Letting Protection Service Scotland') %}
            Website: https://www.lettingprotectionscotland.com/<br>
            Telephone: 0330 303 0031<br>
            {% endif %}
            {% if (tenancyDepositSchemeAdministrator == 'Safedeposits Scotland') %}
